Disk World creator help
load_room_at

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
load_room_at -  This method is used to find a room at the specified coordinates, or to clone and setup a new one if none exists so far.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
object load_room_at(int x,
int y,
int z)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^x%^RESET%^ - the x coordinate of the room (internal coordinate system)
%^BOLD%^y%^RESET%^ - the y coordinate of the room (internal coordinate system)
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the room at those coordinates, or 0 if none can be cloned.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/terrain_map/handler_base.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method is used to find a room at the specified coordinates,
or to clone and setup a new one if none exists so far.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
load_room_at, query_room

.EP

